    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp with a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, this chassis offers exceptional longitudinal and lateral dynamics. The vehicle is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and shows excellent mechanical health, including documented rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement. While the finish shows light patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the subframe and bushings remain tight, ensuring the communicative steering and balanced 50/50 weight distribution remain uncompromised.",
      "price": 34500.0,
